    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped paneer</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1716392934856-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1716392934856-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1716392934856-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-3-1716392934856-x1000.jpg",
