          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-4-1716392947504-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the paneer is golden, reduce the heat to medium-low and add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>with the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>and your<strong> cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add your <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> garam masala</strong> and <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 1 min or until very fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1716392960341-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1716392960341-x400.jpg",
